LanguageData.BloodfeederColonist_Revered.stages.no_bl: Without a bloodfeeder master, we are undirected and lost. We should make a bloodfeeder our leader.
Without a bloodfeeder master, we lack proper direction. We should make a bloodfeeder our leader.
LanguageData.BloodfeederColonist_Revered.stages.blood: The bloodfeeder's presence is a great honor. May they live forever.
LanguageData.BloodfeederColonist_Reviled.stages.blood: One of them walks among us. We should expel the bloodfeeder from our home.
LanguageData.BloodfeederDied_Revered.stages.bloodfeed: The bloodfeeders stand above us, yet one has died here. We will surely be punished for this.
LanguageData.BloodfeederDied_Reviled.stages.bloodfeed: The only good bloodfeeder is a dead one.
LanguageData.Bloodfeeder_ReveredBloodfeeder.stages.re: Let them worship me. Feeding upon them places them below me, as animals are below humans.
LanguageData.Bloodfeeder_ReviledBloodfeeder.stages.bl: I am what I hate. I must rid myself of this curse.
